Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ty!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ty jsi Hakodate z tenisového klubu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.76,Kill_WHITE,TS,0,0,0,,{\fs50\blur0.6\pos(791,512)}Tenisového\N klubu
